'''Ales''' are a category of brewed drinks, usually obtained from [[Bar (location)|bars, pubs and inns]] across the world or [[brewing|brewed]] by players themselves. Most ales restore a little health, but also provide a few [[temporary skill boosts|temporary boosts]] to [[skill]]s, while they also have a drawback on others, usually [[Attack]], [[Strength]] and [[Defence]], which should be considered before they are drunk.

